    "source": "### 🎛️ Define an image-generation model\n\n- Use `ImageInferenceParams` so Data Designer treats this model as an image generator.\n- Image options (size, quality, aspect ratio, etc.) are model-specific; pass them via `extra_body`.",
    "source_html": "<h3>🎛️ Define an image-generation model</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Use <code>ImageInferenceParams</code> so Data Designer treats this model as an image generator.</li>\n<li>Image options (size, quality, aspect ratio, etc.) are model-specific; pass them via <code>extra_body</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n"
